    {"intent_id": "proscons_microservices", "query": "what are the pros and cons of microservices", "response": "Pros: independent deployment, technology flexibility per service, team autonomy, horizontal scaling, fault isolation. Cons: distributed system complexity, network latency, data consistency challenges, operational overhead (monitoring, logging, tracing), harder debugging, service discovery needed. Start monolith, split when you have clear boundaries.", "variant": "list"},
