    {"intent_id": "vs_python_javascript", "query": "should I learn Python or JavaScript", "response": "Python if: data science, AI/ML, automation, scripting, backend, scientific computing. JavaScript if: web development (frontend required), full-stack with one language, mobile (React Native). Both are beginner-friendly. Python has cleaner syntax. JavaScript has more immediate visual results. For maximum employability: learn both — Python first, then JavaScript.", "variant": "short"},
